// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2192 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: fcb823f8-365f-5afa-8556-c502c47e5d02

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
